[[File:Dragon Masks.png|thumb|right|350px|Severin Silrajin and the cult's other [[wyrmspeaker]]s, with the five [[dragon mask]]s.]]
The charismatic cult leader attracted many allies to his cause, including the five powerful wyrmspeakers, and many [[chromatic dragon]]s. Notable among those dragons were [[Vartilingorix]], and even [[Lostmauth]],{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 4}}

He was however still opposed by some members of the cult's "old guard", including the [[Wearer of Purple]] [[Ixas]].{{Cite adventurers league/Shadows Over the Moonsea|5}}

Severin had a [[pseudodragon]] [[familiar]] named [[Nelvik]].
